<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<title>Christen Thompson for Heber City Council</title>
		<meta name="description" content="Campaign website for Christen Thompson, Heber City Council." />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="/src/styles/global.css" />
	</head>
	<body class="bg-gray-50 min-h-screen font-sans">
		<header class="bg-green-900 text-white py-6 shadow">
			<div class="container mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between px-4">
				<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">Christen Thompson for Heber City Council</h1>
				<nav class="mt-4 md:mt-0">
					<a href="/" class="mr-6 hover:underline">Home</a>
					<a href="/about" class="mr-6 hover:underline">About</a>
					<a href="/blog" class="hover:underline">Blog</a>
				</nav>
			</div>
		</header>
		<main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-10">
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
				<!-- Open Space -->
				<div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6 flex flex-col items-center">
					<img src="/images/Heber Valley Rays.jpg" alt="Open Space" class="rounded mb-4 w-full h-40 object-cover" />
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Open Space</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-700 text-center">Protect Heber Valley from urban sprawl through conservation easements, zoning that matches our general plan to preserve the majority of land as open space with public access and follow Midway's example. Put an open space bond on the ballot and preserve what we can for future generations.</p>
				</div>
				<!-- Clean Water -->
				<div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6 flex flex-col items-center">
					<img src="/images/ValleyView.png" alt="Clean Water" class="rounded mb-4 w-full h-40 object-cover" />
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Clean Water</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-700 text-center">Expand our sensitive lands ordinance to protect more drainage areas and Heber Valley's water supply.</p>
				</div>
				<!-- Clean Air -->
				<div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6 flex flex-col items-center">
					<img src="/images/DeerSunrise.png" alt="Clean Air" class="rounded mb-4 w-full h-40 object-cover" />
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Clean Air</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-700 text-center">Work with the county to expand transit. We need a bus going from Provo Airport, through Heber, directly to the Salt Lake City Airport and the reverse.</p>
				</div>
				<!-- Affordability -->
				<div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6 flex flex-col items-center">
					<img src="/images/Timp.jpg" alt="Affordability" class="rounded mb-4 w-full h-40 object-cover" />
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Affordability</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-700 text-center">Having adequate supply and good transportation options can ease the pressure we have on the high cost of living. Keep the building concentrated downtown. The current city council has designated 150 W to 150 E and 1200 S to 900 N as high density, and that's where we should keep the density. Let's make it easier for homeowners to add an additional dwelling unit at their primary residence.</p>
				</div>
				<!-- Trails and Paths -->
				<div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6 flex flex-col items-center">
					<img src="/images/EBike.jpg" alt="Trails and Paths" class="rounded mb-4 w-full h-40 object-cover" />
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Trails and Paths</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-700 text-center">We need better connections within Heber and connecting Heber. Let's follow the county master trail plan and get those trails built along the canals, Center Street, and more. Here is a picture of my ebike commute to Deer Valley :) Don't let a little snow stop you!</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</main>
		<footer class="bg-green-900 text-white py-4 mt-10 text-center">
			&copy; 2025 Christen Thompson for Heber City Council
		</footer>
	</body>
</html>
